          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We decide to withdraw to the safety of the island to the left of the bay. The rocks are immensely slippery but we manage to beach ourselves and the kayak without disaster. We find a sunny perch on a large boulder and melt into the calm that is sunset over lake Malawi.",
